Package de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.utilsV2

Class AgentMeetings

java.lang.Object
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.utilsV2.AgentMeetings
public class AgentMeetings extends Object
The class AgentMeetings contains all the important methods for a AgentMeeting. When two agents have met they will most of the time merge into one group.
Author:
Melinda Betz
